{
  "eventType": "InTransit",
  "location": "Phoenix Hub",
  "notes": "Package in transit to destination"
}

### 9. Transition Status to InTransit
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/parcels/1
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json-patch+json

[
  { "op": "replace", "path": "/status", "value": "InTransit" }
]

### 10. Add Tracking Event - Out For Delivery
